Impale - blade technique
------------------------------------------------------------
Using the impale blade technique, a swashbuckler tries
to inflict deep wounds by following through on each
impaling attack. A swashbuckler must be light on his feet
to successfully make such a deep attack without becoming
excessively vulnerable to counterattack.

Damage increases at each character-level bracket: +45 below Hero,
+56 at Hero, +67 at Legend, +78 at Epic, and +90 at Mythic.

GL: 11
SP:  9 / proc, reduced by Flow
command:  impale
duration: technique mode
